data.description:
Discover the charm of North Hills living in this delightful brick home with a private backyard sanctuary featuring a sparkling pool. The two spacious living areas offer versatility, one with a cozy brick fireplace, and the other ideal for an office space. Entertain guests in the formal dining area or enjoy casual meals in the separate breakfast area overlooking the stunning kitchen. 

This home boasts 4 great-sized bedrooms, with the master bedroom standing out for its spacious layout and a luxurious bathroom. The master bathroom is complete with a garden tub, walk-in shower, and a double vanity sink, while a walk-in closet adds convenience.

This North Hills gem offers a rare opportunity to experience the best of both indoor and outdoor living. With its prime location and enchanting features, this property invites you to make it your own and embrace the North Hills lifestyle. Don't miss out on this chance to call this charming brick home yours!
